Evaluation of the Tokuhashi prognosis score and its modifications in 217 
patients with vertebral metastases.

Ulmar B(1), Huch K, Naumann U, Catalkaya S, Cakir B, Gerstner S, Reichel H.

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopedics, University of Ulm, c/o Rehabilitation Hospital Ulm 
