contagion & schistosomiasis, tumor and etc in 2002 and shifted a lot compared 
with that in 1973. The average life expectancy of residents in Changde was 67.6 
from 1973 to 2002. The average life expectancy of males and females increased 
12.63 and 11.93 years in 2002 compared with those in 1972. In the past 30 years, 
the diseases of respiratory system has greatly influenced the life span of 
residents in Changde.

